
'''Center for Citizen Media'''

URL = http://citmedia.org/

"Our goal is to assist and enhance grassroots media, with a focus on journalism. Why? The democratization of media -- the tools for creating and distributing digital content -- gives us all the ability to publish for a global audience and to collaborate in new ways. We need a robust media ecosystem that helps us all know about the world we live in, so we can make better decisions.
The Center is affiliated with the Graduate School of Journalism at the University of California, Berkeley, and the Berkman Center for Internet & Society at Harvard University Law School."

